data.description: 5 minute access to Charlotte Harbor with your sail or powerboat from this well maintained 3/2/2 home. Entry, kitchen, hallway and doors are extra wide for a spacious feel and provide for wheelchair access if needed. Plenty of areas to entertain as there is a large great room, 20 x 24 screened patio and an upper level deck that is 10 x 25. Approximately 75 feet of heavy duty rip rap seawall with a concrete cap leads you to the 6,000 lb. boat lift that also has an 8 x 20 lower dock  No damage from Ian as the roof was new in 2021. New water heater in 2023. Oversized driveway can handle several vehicles and the detached garage(20 x 24) is equipped with a workbench along with a pedestrian door to the patio. Extensive landscape package includes stone, mature trees, concrete curbing etc.
